Rehn Says Passage of Economic Governance Package Is a Milestone

-- B y   J o n e s   H a y d e n
-- 
2011-09-28T13:18:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/rehn-says-passage-of-economic-governance-package-is-a-milestone.html
European Union Economic and
Monetary Affairs Commissioner  Olli Rehn  said the European
Parliament’s passage of tougher deficit rules is a “milestone”
that represents a fundamental change in euro-area governance.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
